videos.headline: UVA's Ellis lunges for TD
videos.description: Jordan Ellis catches a swing pass and runs for a 6-yard Virginia touchdown.

videos.headline: UVA takes control with a nice TD catch
videos.description: Virginia's Hasise Dubois hauls in a tough catch for a 10-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ohio's Rourke tosses 36-yard TD
videos.description: Bobcats QB Nathan Rourke throws a long 36-yard touchdown pass to Isiah Cox right before halftime.
